Package com.commercetools.importapi.models.common

Interface ImportResource

All Known Subinterfaces:
CategoryImport, CustomerImport, InventoryImport, PriceImport, ProductDraftImport, ProductImport, ProductTypeImport, ProductVariantImport, StandalonePriceImport
All Known Implementing Classes:
CategoryImportImpl, CustomerImportImpl, ImportResourceImpl, InventoryImportImpl, PriceImportImpl, ProductDraftImportImpl, ProductImportImpl, ProductTypeImportImpl, ProductVariantImportImpl, StandalonePriceImportImpl
public interface ImportResource

A representation of the resource to import. Import resources are similar to draft types, but they only support key references. In general, import resources are more granular then regular resources. They are optimized for incremental updates and therefore have a slightly different structure.

Example to create an instance using the builder pattern 

     ImportResource importResource = ImportResource.builder()
             .key("{key}")
             .build()
